        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Not many businesses are great at more than one thing.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Perhaps because it's really hard to do one thing really well.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "More than one only makes it harder.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The lesson is two-fold: given the option, it's better to overdeliver on one thing than to provide multiple options that fall short.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "And, if you're on the receiving end and you have to choose, go with what a business is known for, and what they're good at.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Avoid almost everything else.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}